% Demo purpose: show a contradictory signed condition in one intersection term.
% Expected findings: SG008 WARNING for -fuel_boundary and fuel_boundary.
% Geometry settings: not required for this demo step.
% Scope: independently written, simplified, and not a production reactor model.

surf fuel_boundary cyl 0.0 0.0 0.40
surf system_boundary sqc 0.0 0.0 0.65

cell fuel_cell 0 fuel -fuel_boundary fuel_boundary -system_boundary
cell outside_cell 0 outside system_boundary

mat fuel -10.0
92235.09c -1.0
